## API Versioning

- **Strategy:** {{API_VERSIONING_STRATEGY}} <!-- URL prefix (/api/v1/) or Header -->
- Base path: `{{API_BASE_URL}}`
- Breaking changes require a new version

---

## Standard Error Codes

| Code | HTTP Status | Description |
|---|---|---|
| VALIDATION_ERROR | 400 | Request body or params failed validation |
| UNAUTHORIZED | 401 | Missing or invalid authentication token |
| FORBIDDEN | 403 | Authenticated but insufficient permissions |
| NOT_FOUND | 404 | Resource does not exist or is soft-deleted |
| CONFLICT | 409 | Duplicate entry or state conflict |
| INTERNAL_ERROR | 500 | Unexpected server error |

---

## Pagination

- Default page size: {{DEFAULT_PAGE_SIZE}} (typically 20)
- Max page size: {{MAX_PAGE_SIZE}} (typically 100)
- Query params: `?page=1&limit=20&sort=createdAt&order=desc`
- Filtering: `?status=active&search=keyword`

---

## Rate Limiting

- **Authenticated:** {{RATE_LIMIT_AUTH}} requests/minute
- **Unauthenticated:** {{RATE_LIMIT_UNAUTH}} requests/minute
- Response header: `X-RateLimit-Remaining`

---

## API Documentation

- **Tool:** {{API_DOCS_TOOL}} <!-- Swagger / OpenAPI / Redoc -->
- **URL:** `{{API_DOCS_URL}}`
- Every endpoint must have JSDoc/decorator documentation
- Request/response DTOs define the schema

